  "prompt": "How do I connect my PC's internet to my Windows Phone via USB or via Bluetooth?",
  "response": "To share your PC's internet connection with your Windows Phone, you can use either USB or Bluetooth. Below are the steps for both methods:\n\n---\n\n### **Method 1: Share Internet via USB**\n1. **Connect Your Phone to PC via USB**:\n   - Use a USB cable to connect your Windows Phone to your PC.\n\n2. **Enable Internet Sharing on Your PC**:\n   - On your PC, open **Settings** > **Network & Internet** > **Mobile hotspot**.\n   - Turn on **Share my Internet connection with other devices**.\n   - Choose the network connection you want to share (e.g., Wi-Fi or Ethernet).\n\n3. **Enable USB Tethering on Your Phone**:\n   - On your Windows Phone, go to **Settings** > **Network & wireless** > **Mobile hotspot**.\n   - Enable **USB tethering** or **Internet sharing**.\n   - Your phone should now use the PC\u2019s internet connection.\n\n---\n\n### **Method 2: Share Internet via Bluetooth**\n1. **Pair Your Phone with PC via Bluetooth**:\n   - On your PC, go to **Settings** > **Devices** > **Bluetooth & other devices** and turn on Bluetooth.\n   - On your Windows Phone, go to **Settings** > **Bluetooth** and turn it on.\n   - Pair your phone and PC by following the on-screen instructions.\n\n2. **Enable Internet Sharing on Your PC**:\n   - Open **Settings** > **Network & Internet** > **Mobile hotspot**.\n   - Turn on **Share my Internet connection with other devices**.\n   - Choose the network connection you want to share.\n\n3. **Connect Your Phone to the PC\u2019s Bluetooth Network**:\n   - On your Windows Phone, go to **Settings** > **Bluetooth**.\n   - Select your PC from the list of paired devices and connect to it.\n   - Your phone should now use the PC\u2019s internet connection via Bluetooth.\n\n---\n\n### Notes:\n- Ensure your PC has an active internet connection (Wi-Fi or Ethernet).\n- USB tethering is generally faster and more reliable than Bluetooth.\n- Some Windows Phones may have slightly different settings, but the process should be similar.\n\nLet me know if you need further assistance!",
